| 1 | No authentication/authorization | A01 | 🔴 HIGH | Medium |
| 2 | Missing security headers | A05 | 🔴 HIGH | Low (1 line) |
| 3 | No rate limiting | A04 | 🔴 HIGH | Low |
| 4 | No CORS policy | A05 | 🟠 MEDIUM | Low |
| 5 | No body size limits | A04 | 🟠 MEDIUM | Low |
| 6 | Stack trace leakage | A05 | 🟠 MEDIUM | Low |
| 7 | No logging/monitoring | A09 | 🟠 MEDIUM | Low |
| 8 | Hardcoded configuration | A05 | 🟡 LOW | Low |
| 9 | No 404 handler | A05 | 🟡 LOW | Low |
| 10 | No HTTPS enforcement | A02 | 🟡 LOW | Low |

**Required packages to add:** `helmet`, `cors`, `express-rate-limit`, `morgan`, `jsonwebtoken`

